node.text:
I’ve loved this song since it came out earlier this year. The words “stand up, show up for her” felt like such a needed call to action.

I wanted to share this in honor of #DayOfTheGirl and a reminder to us all: let’s continue to stand up and show up for all of the girls who’ve been rendered incapable of reaching their potential because they are women.

If you can, I encourage you to join me today in donating to @girlsopportunityalliance in support of our next generation of leaders: young women everywhere.
